{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/Konijn_portret.png?t=1737560762\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/Harold.png?t=1737560762\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a little rabbit, while reading the books of rabbit detective Flynn, Harold wanted nothing more than to become a rabbit detective himself!<br><br>And now, he is! <br>Together with his faithful sidekick, the bumblebee Maud, Harold will find anything that has been lost and misplaced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/Maud_portret.png?t=1737560762\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But now, something has been stolen from Harold himself!\u00a0 Will he be able to find out who did it, and why, and solve the mystery of ... <strong>the missing trumpet</strong>?<br><br>Find out in <strong>Harold Rabbit : Finder of Lost Things</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/Harold.png?t=1737560762\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Harold Rabbit : Finder of Lost Things</strong> is a fully hand-drawn point &amp; click adventure for all ages, with an emphasis on fun and comedy.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737560762","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737560762","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/e6e013a1021cc3884219dd5e73732c17d5c35dbc/